We’ve designed our fuel rewards to be... well, rewarding! Every $100 spent with Z Electric, earns you 5L – and it’s scalable. So the more that your electricity bill is, the greater your Fuel Rewards are. Litres are deposited into your Sharetank after each successful payment. Open Sharetank in Z App to redeem, or reward the ones you love.

Occasionally we need to use estimated price or usage data to calculate the above figures. If this happens and we receive meter data at a later date, the difference is applied to your next bill as a charge or credit.
